{
  "stem": "26609.16",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But mama was, was made to look, not to move from where she looked how they beat him until he-- [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] he couldn't call anymore.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Compared with others, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was only hard to think.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I couldn't make myself not to think what happened to all the others.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I thought that if I survive, I will be the only Jewish soul [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in Europe.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] I thought so, that I will be the only one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What I have seen before, I was sure that, that all Jews were killed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't believe that anyone will survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I didn't know then of those concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We never knew anything about it until after the war, we found out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We knew only that they are killing them all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't hungry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'll tell you why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First of all, know Germans are very stingy, all, all Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even as rich as they are, stingy as they are.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] When she fed those people every Thursday, every week, hoards of them came to her place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were city people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she had a farm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So in the city, it was different.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was not enough food in Germany then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Only the top government people had it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Or in the armies, they fed them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They needed them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But otherwise, even Germans didn't have enough, because everything went to the army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- but she was wealthy, the woman with whom I stayed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] she gave what I had.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "As I said, the Poles, she never gave them anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Maybe she gave them some bread.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I don't know about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I wasn't interested, and I never asked.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
